  <h2>How to Sell Cryptocurrency in Kenya</h2>
  <ol>
    <li><strong>Choose a Platform</strong>: Select an exchange or P2P platform</li>
    <li><strong>Create an Account</strong>: Complete KYC verification if required</li>
    <li><strong>Deposit Crypto</strong>: Transfer crypto to your exchange wallet</li>
    <li><strong>Sell</strong>: Place a sell order at market or limit price</li>
    <li><strong>Withdraw KES</strong>: Transfer funds to your M-PESA or bank account</li>
  </ol>

