  <ul>
    <li>‚Ä¢ Capital Gains Tax: 15% on profits from selling crypto</li>
    <li>‚Ä¢ Mining: Taxed as business income</li>
    <li>‚Ä¢ Trading: Considered business income if done frequently</li>
    <li>‚Ä¢ Record Keeping: Maintain records of all transactions</li>
  </ul>
  
